<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 16:10:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列因未决法律问题推迟对 10 月 7 日嫌疑人的起诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-delaying-indictments-of-oct-7-suspects-over-open-legal-questions/00000191-c2a2-d2ba-adb1-e6ab30800000</link><description>尚未确定的方面包括谁将代表嫌疑人以及如此多的案件将给法庭带来的压力，而国际影响和加沙的人质也是问题的一部分</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 15:49:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-delaying-indictments-of-oct-7-suspects-over-open-legal-questions/00000191-c2a2-d2ba-adb1-e6ab30800000</guid></item><item><title>在内塔尼亚胡失态后，以色列重申摩洛哥对西撒哈拉的主权</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-reaffirms-moroccan-sovereignty-of-western-sahara-after-netanyahu-gaffe/00000191-c25b-d870-a59d-e67b87690000</link><description>在新闻发布会上，内塔尼亚胡展示了一张大型中东和北非数字地图，其中摩洛哥南部被标记为西撒哈拉。以色列于 2023 年承认摩洛哥对争议领土的主权，以换取恢复外交关系</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 15:01:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-reaffirms-moroccan-sovereignty-of-western-sahara-after-netanyahu-gaffe/00000191-c25b-d870-a59d-e67b87690000</guid></item><item><title>瑞安航空暂停以色列航班至 10 月 26 日，跳过高需求假期季节</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/ryanair-halts-israel-flights-until-october-26-skipping-high-demand-holiday-season/00000191-c230-d2ba-adb1-e6b98bdc0000</link><description>德国汉莎航空将于周四恢复飞往特拉维夫的航班；对于消费者来说，瑞安航空的决定将减少假期期间的航班供应，可能会推高机票价格</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 14:26:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/ryanair-halts-israel-flights-until-october-26-skipping-high-demand-holiday-season/00000191-c230-d2ba-adb1-e6b98bdc0000</guid></item><item><title>“时间不多了；美国驻以色列特使在人质协议推动中警告称，将没有生命可救</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/there-wont-be-lives-left-to-save-u-s-envoy-to-israel-warns-in-hostage-deal-push/00000191-c1e4-dd1b-a7db-f7fef14f0000</link><description>卢大使反驳了内塔尼亚胡关于以色列国防军从加沙和费城走廊全面撤军是协议初始阶段的一部分的说法：“协议中没有提到费城走廊；起草框架时甚至没有考虑到这一点”</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 11:35:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/there-wont-be-lives-left-to-save-u-s-envoy-to-israel-warns-in-hostage-deal-push/00000191-c1e4-dd1b-a7db-f7fef14f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡受到全球谴责，忙于躲避破坏人质交易的指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/rattled-by-global-rebuke-netanyahu-scrambles-to-fend-off-charges-of-sabotaging-gaza-deal/00000191-c140-d2e0-a7d5-ddd270f10000</link><description>除了与外媒举行新闻发布会外，内塔尼亚胡还派了自己的心腹罗恩·德尔默前往美国媒体讨论人质谈判，因为总理担心美国媒体会更多地关注人质家属对他的批评</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 10:34:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/rattled-by-global-rebuke-netanyahu-scrambles-to-fend-off-charges-of-sabotaging-gaza-deal/00000191-c140-d2e0-a7d5-ddd270f10000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查显示，大多数以色列人支持审查加沙战争社交媒体帖子，揭露犹太与阿拉伯之间的分歧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/poll-majority-of-israelis-back-censoring-gaza-war-posts-exposing-jewish-arab-divide/00000191-c119-de0a-afd5-d959c4d20000</link><description>民意调查发现，政治分歧进一步影响了对审查制度的看法。在以色列右翼人士中，76% 的人希望封锁支持加沙平民的帖子，而左翼人士中只有 25% 的人愿意</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 09:27:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/poll-majority-of-israelis-back-censoring-gaza-war-posts-exposing-jewish-arab-divide/00000191-c119-de0a-afd5-d959c4d20000</guid></item><item><title>卡梅尔·盖特的家人授权播放哈马斯被囚禁的视频：“内塔尼亚胡判处她死刑”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/carmel-gats-family-authorizes-airing-captivity-video-netanyahu-sentenced-her-to-death/00000191-c0a9-dffe-abf9-fdff26310000</link><description>39 岁的盖特 (Gat) 来自贝埃里基布兹 (Kibbutz Be&amp;#39;eri)，于 10 月 7 日被绑架。获释的人质称，她主持瑜伽和冥想课程，以帮助他们保持理智。她计划在人质协议的初始阶段被释放</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 06:04:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/carmel-gats-family-authorizes-airing-captivity-video-netanyahu-sentenced-her-to-death/00000191-c0a9-dffe-abf9-fdff26310000</guid></item><item><title>“哈里斯同情亲哈马斯的民主党人”：副总统拜登在共和党犹太会议上抨击以色列政策</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/on-first-night-of-gop-jewish-confab-speakers-assail-biden-and-harris-over-israel-policies/00000191-c02b-d2e0-a7d5-ddfb24a30000</link><description>拉斯维加斯共和党犹太大会的代表们指责现任政府为哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击提供了便利，让反犹太主义在国内愈演愈烈，并且未能勇敢地面对伊朗</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 03:38:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/on-first-night-of-gop-jewish-confab-speakers-assail-biden-and-harris-over-israel-policies/00000191-c02b-d2e0-a7d5-ddfb24a30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称其击毙了七名约旦河西岸武装分子；八枚火箭弹和无人机瞄准以色列北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article-live/u-s-can-ensure-israeli-security-if-idf-withdraws-from-philadelphi-route-official-says/00000191-bffd-d26b-abfd-bfff57690000</link><description>国际刑事法院首席检察官为内塔尼亚胡、勇敢逮捕令辩护：“我已经看到证据” ■ 慕尼黑袭击以色列领事馆：枪手是当局已知的伊斯兰分子 ■ 以色列国防军：向以色列北部发射火箭弹和八架无人机；无人员伤亡 ■ 加沙卫生部：以色列拒绝协调医疗队入境进行脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种 ■ 美国高级官员：如果以色列国防军从费城撤军，我们可以确保以色列的安全</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 02:31:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article-live/u-s-can-ensure-israeli-security-if-idf-withdraws-from-philadelphi-route-official-says/00000191-bffd-d26b-abfd-bfff57690000</guid></item><item><title>杀死疑似小偷的基布兹安全小组成员不会面临审判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/kibbutz-security-squad-member-who-killed-suspected-thief-wont-face-trial/00000191-bf0b-d2e0-a7d5-bfdb3da80000</link><description>检察官结案，称有证据支持枪手在射杀一名持刀的贝都因青年时出于自卫的说法。受害人家属表示将上诉</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 22:07:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/kibbutz-security-squad-member-who-killed-suspected-thief-wont-face-trial/00000191-bf0b-d2e0-a7d5-bfdb3da80000</guid></item><item><title>被释放的人质敦促以色列总统谴责内塔尼亚胡的玩忽职守</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/former-hostage-urges-israeli-president-to-call-out-netanyahus-dereliction-of-duty/00000191-bef7-d9c6-a997-beff55930000</link><description>利亚特·阿齐利在前总统西蒙·佩雷斯的官方纪念仪式上发表讲话：“内塔尼亚胡反对我们支持人质协议的以色列公民，并将我们视为威胁——这是他政治生存所需的毒药。”我们是一个被内外破坏者绑架的国家”</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 21:57:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/former-hostage-urges-israeli-president-to-call-out-netanyahus-dereliction-of-duty/00000191-bef7-d9c6-a997-beff55930000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击中丧生的一个以色列家庭的四名成员在贝埃里基布兹安息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/four-members-of-one-israeli-family-killed-on-october-7-laid-to-rest-in-kibbutz-beeri/00000191-be6a-dd1b-a7db-bffe74000000</link><description>10 月 7 日被谋杀的 Heztroni 家族的四名成员被重新安葬在贝埃里基布兹：12 岁的双胞胎 Liel 和 Yanai，以及抚养他们的年迈的祖父母 Ayala 和 Avia</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 19:51:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/four-members-of-one-israeli-family-killed-on-october-7-laid-to-rest-in-kibbutz-beeri/00000191-be6a-dd1b-a7db-bffe74000000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯并不是以色列内部裂痕的始作俑者，分裂也不仅仅是外部敌人造成的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-04/ty-article/.highlight/how-to-stop-peaceniks-from-falling-into-hamas-trap-of-holding-israeli-leaders-to-account/00000191-be0c-de0a-afd5-fe4c2b510000</link><description>毫无疑问，哈马斯利用人质进行宣传。但内塔尼亚胡所说的哈马斯利用内部分歧在以色列制造分裂并不是哈马斯的发明，这种分裂不仅仅是外部敌人造成的</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 19:26:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-04/ty-article/.highlight/how-to-stop-peaceniks-from-falling-into-hamas-trap-of-holding-israeli-leaders-to-account/00000191-be0c-de0a-afd5-fe4c2b510000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家档案馆直到 2089 年才会披露内塔尼亚胡寄出的信件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-state-archives-wont-reveal-letters-sent-by-netanyahu-until-2089/00000191-be0f-dc3b-a7df-ff5f24fd0000</link><description>档案馆以隐私问题为由，密封了内塔尼亚胡写给多位知名人士的私人信件，尽管此前已批准公开类似的信件。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 18:33:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-state-archives-wont-reveal-letters-sent-by-netanyahu-until-2089/00000191-be0f-dc3b-a7df-ff5f24fd0000</guid></item><item><title>伴随脊髓灰质炎疫苗进入加沙的阴谋论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/the-conspiracy-theory-accompanying-the-polio-vaccine-into-gaza/00000191-bdfc-dd1b-a7db-bffe3f160000</link><description>备受瞩目的加沙活动家 Bisan Owda 并不信任以色列已经签署的脊髓灰质炎疫苗。但包括医疗专业人士在内的许多网上人士建议这位获得艾美奖提名的网红删除她的视频并道歉，以免脊髓灰质炎在拉斯维加斯大道蔓延</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 18:16:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/the-conspiracy-theory-accompanying-the-polio-vaccine-into-gaza/00000191-bdfc-dd1b-a7db-bffe3f160000</guid></item><item><title>“恐惧感”：哥伦比亚大学新年伊始，犹太和以色列学生保持警惕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/sense-of-dread-jewish-and-israeli-students-wary-as-columbia-u-starts-new-year/00000191-bd2e-de3d-abb7-ff6fd3e60000</link><description>虽然纽约常春藤盟校坚称已采取新程序来制止反犹太主义和去年加沙战争引发的丑陋场面的重演，但犹太学生和教职员工表示，他们已经看到了事情“正在好转”的迹象。他们离开的地方&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 17:45:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/sense-of-dread-jewish-and-israeli-students-wary-as-columbia-u-starts-new-year/00000191-bd2e-de3d-abb7-ff6fd3e60000</guid></item><item><title>“内塔尼亚胡的母亲对拉宾批准恩德培而不是达成协议感到愤怒”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahus-mom-was-furious-at-rabin-for-approving-entebbe-instead-of-reaching-a-deal/00000191-bcce-de3d-abb7-feef359a0000</link><description>新系列纪录片《人质》的创作者讲述了我们如何遭遇 100 多名以色列人质在哈马斯的囚禁中死去近一年的情况</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 17:37:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahus-mom-was-furious-at-rabin-for-approving-entebbe-instead-of-reaching-a-deal/00000191-bcce-de3d-abb7-feef359a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质家属称亲内塔尼亚胡频道告诉他们联盟胜过协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-say-pro-netanyahu-channel-told-them-coalition-trumps-deal/00000191-bd90-dffe-abf9-bdff65c90000</link><description>Channel 14 高管告诉家属，释放亲人的协议不会达成，因为这会导致政府垮台</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 17:11:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-say-pro-netanyahu-channel-told-them-coalition-trumps-deal/00000191-bd90-dffe-abf9-bdff65c90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 334 天：大约 70 枚火箭从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-334-some-70-rockets-fired-at-north-israel-from-lebanon/00000191-bdf0-dc3b-a7df-fff0b3620001</link><description>政府消息人士告诉《国土报》，内塔尼亚胡几周前决定不达成释放人质协议，并以费城走廊为借口破坏谈判。据《华尔街日报》报道，预计将提交更详细的人质/停火协议草案 ■ 这是战争开始 334 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 17:00:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-334-some-70-rockets-fired-at-north-israel-from-lebanon/00000191-bdf0-dc3b-a7df-fff0b3620001</guid></item><item><title>为什么哈马斯试图隐瞒被以色列杀害的武装分子人数</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-hamas-tries-to-hide-the-number-of-its-members-killed/00000191-bd7b-d13c-a39b-bfff809b0000</link><description>所有加沙人都知道不要发布被杀的哈马斯战士的信息，任何违反这一规则的人都有可能给该组织以及以色列带来麻烦</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 16:57:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-hamas-tries-to-hide-the-number-of-its-members-killed/00000191-bd7b-d13c-a39b-bfff809b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>